reviewText: I did not know that they even made movies to watch on a psp.  I think this is a great item Brand new. Just what I wanted!
The little UMD version is so cool -  video is crisp and brings my PSP to life. A collection of one of the funniest TV series of its time. Perfect for anyone travelling with their PSP.
